I '''Phyllis Dorothy James, Baroness James of Holland Park''', [[Order of the British Empire|OBE]], [[Royal Society of Arts|FRSA]], [[Royal Society of Literature|FRSL]] (mibait 3 Agosto 1920), a keraklan dang ausan '''P.&nbsp;D. James''', metung yang Ingles a talasulat krimen ampong [[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]] [[life peer]] king [[House of Lords]], a pikabaluan dili king serie da reng nobelang detektib nung nu deng manimunang tauan pulis la, ampo ing poetang i [[Adam Dalgliesh]].<ref>[http://www.parliament.uk/directories/house_of_lords_information_office/alphabetical_list_of_members.cfm#J UK Parliament – Alphabetical List of Members].</ref>

